Name = Main - Tutorial Mission
Introduction = "You're the new pilot? Excellent! We have a situation at the nearby mining outpost that we would like you to look into. But first, some basics."#"Since pirate attacks have gotten more and more common, we strongly recommend that all new recruits take our combat simulation program."
