EventText3 = [Rebel] "All here? Good."#"We'll move as one unit until we have passed the Alliance's defenses around the station."#"Then we'll split up and search for that scientist."#"When he is found, send a signal to all others, and we will all try to pull out as quickly as possible."#"This is a high-risk mission. I doubt that all of us will come back."#"But I'm sure that some of us will, and that they will continue to do what they can for the people."#"I have no more words for you. Good luck friends."
