EventText8 = [Rebel] "Seems like most of us got through. We are tougher than they think!"#"Now, let's search the station."#"If you find Ente, send the signal. If you receive the signal, pull out as quickly as possible."#[SAIR] "Let's see. Let's explore that smaller building outside the complex."
EventText9 = You quickly walk into the building, looking around, searching for the man in the picture you saw.#A man appears in one of the door openings. He looks surprised, and a bit nervous. You ask him if he is Ente.#[Ente] "Well, yes, I am."#"I must say I am a bit surprised by your visit. Can you tell me, who might you be?"#...#"You are here to bring me to the Rebel Station you say?"#"But your eyes tell me something else."#"You don't really know why you are here. You are confused. You wonder what's really going on."#"As you probably know, I am part of a group of scientists researching Murt."#"We are developing and testing scanners to detect and locate large quantities of Murt."#"Up until now, only small amounts have been found at a time around the system."#"Up until recently, that is."#"Our scans have shown us an asteroid containing a massive amount of Murt.#"It is thousands of times more than what we have found up until now combined. It is an unimaginable source of power."#"In the right hands, it would be an immense help for the people of the sector."#"In the wrong hands... It could be used for such destruction."#"..."#"You realize the problem here, don't you?"#"Currently, the whole sector is in a state of conflict. Rebels and Alliance struggle for control."#"Which way is better? I can't say. What I know is that, as it looks now, Murt will be used as a tool of war."#"We must put the Murt to use, but we must put it to good use."#"So what is my suggestion? We must hide the Murt."#"Hide it until the sector is ready to handle it."#"When the sector stabilizes one day, in ten or a hundred years, we can bring it out in the open."#Ente eyes you curiously.#"You know. I am telling you all this for a reason."#"I want your cooperation."#"We must hide Murt away before that happens."#"To do this, you will need to access one of our information centrals."#"There you will find information about where to find the technology, as well as the exact location of the meteor."#"You should bring me to the Rebel Base. Then you should go to the information hub."#"I will not leak crucial information until I know that you have finished your mission."#"By then it will be too late for them to do anything about it."#"Let's go"#The strange man hurries before you up into the ship.
